(Hey Tankor, could you reply to my post in Blades VS Noble?  And also your 
Obsidian character defeated my Modem character in a match.  I'll include both 
of those posts at the end of this one)

Lash:



Moving quickly, his whip dragging on the ground, Lash sidestepped the 
incoming blasts, two laser bolts lancing out from his optic sensors at 
Penguin2's chest.


(Modem Losing to Obsidian: 

Modem/Otyebis Staff:



The five warheads struck dead on, blowing Modem to smithereens, the Nebulan 
instantly fried like chicken in a vat of boiling grease.

"The winner is Obsidian, congrats." the announcer said, the crowd in the 
stands instantly leaving to go look at a different fight.

A team of soldiers came out, half gathering the liquidy remains of Modem, the 
other half approaching Obsidian.

"Follow us." the said, heading for the only visible exit out of this arena.)

(Fight between Blades and Noble:


Blades:



Reaching out with his left arm he holds it aloft, waiting for Noble to shake 
it.  "Good luck.")
